content:
alexcrichton opened PR #5393 from fix-bulid to main:

A mistake was made in the publication of wit-parser where a breaking change was made without bumping its major version, causing build issues on main if wit-parser is updated. This commit updates wit-parser to the latest and we'll handle breaking changes better next time.

Closes #5390
